.SH NAME
apex \- Unified Markdown processor supporting CommonMark, GFM,
MultiMarkdown, and Kramdown
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[B]apex\f[R] [\f[I]options\f[R]] [\f[I]file\f[R]]
.PP
